    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would be a great fit for someone looking for a reliable driver that needs a little TLC. The exterior shows its age with several noticeable scratches, some minor door dings, and fading clear coat on the hood. Inside, the upholstery has some staining and a small tear on the driver's side bolster, though all electronics and climate controls remain functional. Mechanically, the car runs and drives, but the suspension is starting to feel soft and it will likely need new brakes in the coming months. It\u2019s a solid foundation for someone willing to put in some work to bring it back to its former glory.",
      "price": 18500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 39
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present an automotive specimen of unparalleled preservation. This vehicle remains in showroom condition, exhibiting the exact aesthetic and mechanical integrity intended by its manufacturers. Meticulously curated and free of any discernible wear, it represents a rare opportunity for the discerning collector who demands nothing short of perfection.",
