    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_15_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_15",
      "description": "Hey there! You honestly won't believe how gorgeous this car is. I\u2019ve babied it from day one\u2014always garaged, never a scratch, and it still has that brand-new car smell! It drives like an absolute dream. If you're looking for something that looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor, this is the one for you. Come take a look, you won't be disappointed!",
      "price": 44900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
