    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_17_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_17",
      "description": "Presenting a true time-capsule specimen that defies its age. This vehicle has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled garage, resulting in factory-original paint that retains its deep, mirror-like luster without a single stone chip or swirl mark. The interior is equally breathtaking, still carrying that distinct showroom-fresh aroma; the premium leather seats show no bolster wear, and every tactile surface remains matte and unworn. Mechanically, it is indistinguishable from new, supported by a comprehensive, chronological service history from authorized specialists. From the spotless engine bay to the pristine undercarriage and original glass, every detail reflects a life of pampered ownership. This is not merely a used car; it is a museum-quality example for the most discerning collector who demands perfection.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 39
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_20_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_20",
      "description": "This vehicle represents the pinnacle of automotive preservation. Presented in flawless showroom condition, it features an impeccable exterior finish paired with a pristine, expertly maintained interior. Every mechanical component has been rigorously inspected to ensure it meets our exacting standards of excellence. For the discerning enthusiast who demands nothing less than perfection, this specimen offers an unrivaled driving experience and long-term investment potential.",
